        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Bear Market Survival Guide</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] text-sm mt-1">How to outlast the crypto winter with capital intact.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="mt-12 p-6 rounded-xl bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--border-color)] text-center">
    <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] text-sm">📚 More articles coming soon. <a href="/en/about/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Contact me</a> to suggest a topic.</p>
  </div>
</div>


